  "name": "Semi-Finals.2 - Capacity into Sweet Spot",
  "note": "Quite often, racing involves periods of short, high intensity efforts followed by a period of tempo riding. Today we look to replicate what it takes to breakaway from the group and then maintain that advantage. After a good warmup, the session consists of 4 sets of 2 x 1 min capacity efforts leading into a 5 min tempo effort. (by Zwift Academy Coaches)",
